  },
  "lyrics": [
    {
      "time": 2.879,
      "time_str": "00:02.879",
      "text": "When I was young I'd listen to the radio",
      "translation": "我还年轻的时候， 喜欢听收音机"
    },
    {
      "time": 8.918,
      "time_str": "00:08.918",
      "text": "Waiting for my favorite songs",
      "translation": "等待我最喜欢的歌曲"
    },
    {
      "time": 14.559,
      "time_str": "00:14.559",
      "text": "When they played I'd sing along",
      "translation": "当他们演奏时，我会随之吟唱"
    },
    {
      "time": 19.259,
      "time_str": "00:19.259",
      "text": "It made me smile",
      "translation": "这使我心情欢畅"
    },
    {
      "time": 23.909,
      "time_str": "00:23.909",
      "text": "Those were such happy times and not so long ago",
      "translation": "那些是多么幸福的时光！就在不久以前"
    },
    {
      "time": 32.298,
      "time_str": "00:32.298",
      "text": "how I wondered where they'd gone",
      "translation": "我想知道它们曾去何处"
    },
    {
      "time": 37.89,
      "time_str": "00:37.890",
      "text": "But they're back again just like a long lost friend",
      "translation": "而今它们再次出现，就像失散的旧友重逢"
    },
    {
      "time": 43.979,
      "time_str": "00:43.979",
      "text": "all the songs I loved so well",
      "translation": "所有的歌曲我都如此的喜爱"
    },
    {
      "time": 49.239,
      "time_str": "00:49.239",
      "text": "Every shalalala every wo'wo",
      "translation": "每一句sha-la-la-la每一句wo-wo"
    },
    {
      "time": 55.829,
      "time_str": "00:55.829",
      "text": "Still shines",
      "translation": "依旧闪烁"
    },
    {
      "time": 61.679,
      "time_str": "01:01.679",
      "text": "Every shing-a-ling-a-ling",
      "translation": "每一句shing-a-ling-a-ling"
    },
    {
      "time": 64.249,
      "time_str": "01:04.249",
      "text": "That they're starting to sing",
      "translation": "就在他们放声歌唱时"
    },
    {
      "time": 66.99,
      "time_str": "01:06.990",
      "text": "So fine",
      "translation": "如此美妙"
    },
    {
      "time": 73.119,
      "time_str": "01:13.119",
      "text": "When they get to the part",
      "translation": "当他们唱到一个地方"
    },
    {
      "time": 75.669,
      "time_str": "01:15.669",
      "text": "Where he's breaking her heart",
      "translation": "他令她伤心断肠"
    },
    {
      "time": 79.9,
      "time_str": "01:19.900",
      "text": "It can really make me cry",
      "translation": "这真能叫我哭出来"
    },
    {
      "time": 84.2,
      "time_str": "01:24.200",
      "text": "Just like before",
      "translation": "正如从前一样"
    },
    {
      "time": 89.289,
      "time_str": "01:29.289",
      "text": "It's yesterday once more",
      "translation": "仿佛昔日又重来"
    },
    {
      "time": 98.89,
      "time_str": "01:38.890",
      "text": "(shoobie do lang lang)",
      "translation": "无比惆怅"
    },
    {
      "time": 102.178,
      "time_str": "01:42.178",
      "text": "Looking back on how it was in years gone by",
      "translation": "回头看岁月如何消逝"
    },
    {
      "time": 107.828,
      "time_str": "01:47.828",
      "text": "And the good times that I had",
      "translation": "这些过去的好时光"
    },
    {
      "time": 114.19,
      "time_str": "01:54.190",
      "text": "Makes today seem rather sad",
      "translation": "使今天显得令人哀伤"
    },
    {
      "time": 118.349,
      "time_str": "01:58.349",
      "text": "So much has changed",
      "translation": "一切都已不再"
    },
    {
      "time": 127.39,
      "time_str": "02:07.390",
      "text": "It was songs of love that I would sing to then",
      "translation": "那时我跟唱着这些爱之歌"
    },
    {
      "time": 131.228,
      "time_str": "02:11.228",
      "text": "and I'd memorize each word",
      "translation": "我会记住每一句歌词"
    },
    {
      "time": 136.168,
      "time_str": "02:16.168",
      "text": "Those old melodies still sound so good to me",
      "translation": "那些熟悉的旋律，在我听来还是那么好"
    },
    {
      "time": 143.198,
      "time_str": "02:23.198",
      "text": "As they melt the years away",
      "translation": "好像他们把岁月融消"
    },
    {
      "time": 149.39,
      "time_str": "02:29.390",
      "text": "Every shalalala every wo'wo still shines",
      "translation": "每一句sha-la-la-la每一句wo-wo仍闪烁"
    },
    {
      "time": 159.998,
      "time_str": "02:39.998",
      "text": "Every shing-a-ling-a-ling",
      "translation": "每一句shing-a-ling-a-ling"
    },
    {
      "time": 162.327,
      "time_str": "02:42.327",
      "text": "That they're starting to sing",
      "translation": "就在他们放声歌唱时"
    },
    {
      "time": 165.648,
      "time_str": "02:45.648",
      "text": "So fine",
      "translation": "如此美妙"
    },
    {
      "time": 171.577,
      "time_str": "02:51.577",
      "text": "All my best memories come back clearly to me",
      "translation": "我所有美好的记忆清晰的重现"
    },
    {
      "time": 176.868,
      "time_str": "02:56.868",
      "text": "Some can even make me cry",
      "translation": "有一些仍能使我哭出来"
    },
    {
      "time": 181.879,
      "time_str": "03:01.879",
      "text": "Just like before",
      "translation": "正如从前一样"
    },
    {
      "time": 187.698,
